# 1️⃣7️⃣ COMMON FAILURE POINTS (TO DESIGN AGAINST)

❌ Early financial disclosure
❌ Single-person opening authority
❌ Weak encryption key storage
❌ Manual override without audit trail
❌ Lack of immutable opening report
❌ Uncontrolled visibility to unauthorized roles

System design must eliminate these risks.

---

